            <title>[LU-10050] Problem in lod_declare_update_plain()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10050</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;An extra &apos;&amp;amp;&apos; was in lod_declare_update_plain () as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;comp_v1 = (struct lov_comp_md_v1 *)&amp;amp;info-&amp;gt;lti_buf.lb_buf;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This will cause invalid memory region to be accessed in replay path.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
